name: Super Delivery
description:
Super delivery is a 2D runner, you are a superpowered delivery girl a flying ability. Deliver the pizza through skies filled with other dangerous superheroes.

Instructions

W/A/S/D to move

or

Click on the screen to make delivery girl mouse to your mouse location
